Class ColumnModelEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event.Event
        • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.event.ColumnModelEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ColumnModelEvent
extends Event
    ColumnModelEvent is used to notify listeners that a table column model has changed, such as a column was added, removed, or moved.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
